===变化===
*M＆M的巧克力片饼干，用M＆M巧克力代替巧克力片。
*雙重巧克力饼干，直接使用加入熔化巧克力或是可可的面团製作饼干<ref>[http://www.foodnetwork.com/food/recipes/recipe/0,1977,FOOD_9936_4318,00.html Chocolate Chocolate Chip cookie] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070613154514/http://www.foodnetwork.com/food/recipes/recipe/0%2C1977%2CFOOD_9936_4318%2C00.html |date=2007-06-13 }} recipe on FoodTV.com</ref>。也有些變化是用[[白巧克力|白巧克力]]或是[[花生醬|花生醬]]片代替巧克力片<ref>[http://allrecipes.com/Recipe/White-Chip-Chocolate-Cookies/Detail.aspx White Chip Chocolate Cookie recipe] {{Wayback|url=http://allrecipes.com/Recipe/White-Chip-Chocolate-Cookies/Detail.aspx |date=20150818192415 }} on AllFood.com</ref><ref>[http://allrecipes.com/Recipe/Chewy-Chocolate-Peanut-Butter-Chip-Cookies/Detail.aspx Chocolate Peanut Butter Chip Cookie recipe] {{Wayback|url=http://allrecipes.com/Recipe/Chewy-Chocolate-Peanut-Butter-Chip-Cookies/Detail.aspx |date=20150824023231 }} on AllFood.com</ref>。
*夏威夷豆饼干中有[[夏威夷豆|夏威夷豆]]及白巧克力碎片<ref>[http://allrecipes.com/Recipe/Macadamia-Nut-Chocolate-Chip-Cookies/Detail.aspx Macadamia Nut Chocolate Chip Cookies] {{Wayback|url=http://allrecipes.com/Recipe/Macadamia-Nut-Chocolate-Chip-Cookies/Detail.aspx |date=20150812221905 }} recipe on AllFoods.com</ref>。
*巧克力片花生饼干用花生酱的面团代替香草味的面团。
*其它变化包括不同尺寸和形状的巧克力片，例如純巧克力片或是牛奶巧克力片。因此在口感及风味上會有些不同。

